<%- include("partials/header"); -%>
<div class="ui segment" id="header" style="margin-top: 50px; height: 50%">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2.5em">Welcome to the COVID-19 information system.</h1>
  <h3>We're here to help you through the COVID-19 wars</h3>
  <h4>Let's save the world!</h4>
</div>
<div class="ui container">
  <div class="segment">
    <h2>First off, what's coronavirus (COVID-19)</h2>
    <p>
      Coronaviruses (CoV) are a large family of viruses that cause illness
      ranging from the common cold to more severe diseases such as Middle East
      Respiratory Syndrome (MERS-CoV) and Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome
      (SARS-CoV).
    </p>
    <h2 style="text-align: center">Symptoms</h2>
    <div class="ui stackable two column grid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="ui column segment">
          <p>Common signs of infection include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay=".5s"
              ></i>
              Fever
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="1s"
              ></i>
              Cough
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="1.5s"
              ></i>
              Shortness of breath
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="2s"
              ></i>
              Breathing difficulties
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ui column segment">
          <p>In more severe cases, infection can cause:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay=".5s"
              ></i>
              Pneumonia
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="1s"
              ></i
              >Severe acute respiratory syndrome
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="1.5s"
              ></i>
              Kidney failure
            </li>
            <li>
              <i
                class="fas fa-chevron-right wow fadeInLeft"
                data-wow-delay="2s"
              ></i>
              Death
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include("partials/footer"); -%>
